entral collisions. The published\n$p(N_{\\mathrm{ch}})$ is also used to estimate $\\Delta R_{\\left\\langle\np_{\\mathrm{T}}\\right\\rangle}$ for mean transverse momentum, which is\nnon-negligible compared with $R_{\\left\\langle p_{\\mathrm{T}}\\right\\rangle}-1$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2022 18:18:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 14:43:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-01"}
