ur method can be\nstraightforwardly implemented in experimental setups with globally-coherent\nqubit control and qubit-resolved single-shot read-out and is thus applicable to\nother physical systems such as neutral atoms in tweezer arrays.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2022 18:23:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 19 Feb 2023 21:10:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-21"}
